    {
      "name": "[B1] Warehouse",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>The lower level holds recently filled casks along with wood for the ovens and grain stockpiled for brewing. When barley is being germinated, the room can get very crowded.</p>",
        "format": 1
