    {
      "name": "[B4] Mash Tuns",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>Malted barley and oats are soaked in two wooden tuns to produce the wort. A trough carries the wort to the fermenters.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
