    },
    {
      "name": "[B5] Ovens",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>Two large ovens are used to roast the germinated barley. They also heat water to a boil in large copper cauldrons above them.</p>\n<p> </p>",
        "format": 1
      },
