    {
      "name": "[B6] Brew Kettles",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>These large copper cauldrons are filled with well water and heated by the ovens below. The brewery has its own internal well to help ensure the water is kept free of contamination. Portable troughs can be used to direct the water from the well across to the far kettle.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
